{"data":[{"date":"22:05 08/07","title":"S\u00f4i s\u1ee5c c\u00f9ng clip nh\u1ea1c ch\u1ebf c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng cho World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/soi-suc-cung-clip-nhac-che-co-dong-cho-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch hay nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n28 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Argentina r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Brazil \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. D\u00f9 bu\u1ed3n, vui, h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng hay th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac kh\u00f4n t\u1ea3 m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 mang \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 trong g\u1ea7n 1 th\u00e1ng qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa l\u00e0 World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 h\u01a1i ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u max h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, max k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f2a chung trong s\u1ef1 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ca kh\u00fac nh\u1ea1c ch\u1ebf &quot;Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean b\u00f3ng&quot; d\u1ef1a theo b\u00e0i h\u00e1t &quot;Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac&quot; nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n World Cup 2018!<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/8/nhac-che-khong-quen-bong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>L\u1eddi nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n: Tika T\u00f9ng Anh</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ta kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ch\u01b0a xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay anh em ta ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nB\u00e0n l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a n\u0103m nay<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo n\u0103m nay ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00ecnh qu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u<br>\r\nTh\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i anh ra v\u1ec1<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac, n\u0103m nay Si l\u1ea1i u\u1ea5t \u1ee9c<br>\r\nAnh ch\u01a1i trong s\u1ef1 c\u00f4 \u0111\u01a1n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi bao nhi\u00eau th\u00e1ng n\u0103m \u1edf b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i anh<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd Anh n\u0103m nay l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br>\r\nTuy qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u si\u00eau sao<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i v\u1eabn v\u00f4 v\u00f2ng trong<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i r\u00ecnh r\u00ecnh<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh<br>\r\nAnh em c\u00f9ng nhau&nbsp; ta th\u00e2u \u0111\u00eam<br>\r\nD\u1eabu bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t<br>\r\nMai anh em \u0111i l\u00e0m r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i<br>\r\nB\u00ean ly r\u01b0\u1ee3u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u1eaft ta ng\u1eebng xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nS\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <br>\r\nS\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec <br>\r\nTh\u00f4i ta n\u1edd \u0111i ta xem ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\nC\u1ed1 th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng v\u1eady<br>\r\nAnh em ta tuy m\u1ec7t r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u1ed5 ng\u1ea9ng \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\nXem b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i d\u00e0i<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ta kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ch\u01b0a xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay anh em ta ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nB\u00e0n l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a n\u0103m nay<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay anh em tin n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c<br>\r\nV\u1eady m\u00e0 gi\u1edd h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc lu\u00f4n<br>\r\nUruguay kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua France<br>\r\nH\u1ecd nh\u1eadn thua ra v\u1ec1<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac, T\u00e2y ban nha ph\u1ea3i thua Nga<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ean \u0111\u00e2u<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf n\u00ean th\u00f4i 4 n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp n\u1eefa, Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i Win \u0111\u00e2u<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf n\u00ean th\u00f4i ch\u00fang ta c\u1ee9 \u0111i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i r\u00ecnh r\u00ecnh<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh<br>\r\nAnh em c\u00f9ng nhau&nbsp; ta th\u00e2u \u0111\u00eam<br>\r\nGi\u1eabu bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t<br>\r\nMai anh em \u0111i l\u00e0m r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i<br>\r\nB\u00ean ly r\u01b0\u1ee3u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u1eaft ta ng\u1eebng xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nS\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <br>\r\nS\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec <br>\r\nTh\u00f4i ta n\u1edd \u0111i ta xem ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\nC\u1ed1 th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng v\u1eady<br>\r\nAnh em ta tuy m\u1ec7t r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u1ed5 ng\u1ea9ng \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\nXem b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i d\u00e0i<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1047","checkdouble":"190716"},{"date":"22:12 08/07","title":"HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/cong-phng_kv8pj4j0zvgm1iag592kifipy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ed1 \u00fd ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n va ch\u1ea1m ng\u00e3 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee9ng xa qu\u00e1, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 nh\u01b0ng h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi v\u00e0 n\u00e9m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4i b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HAGL l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Duy Thanh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi HAGL nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u00eam v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng T\u00e2n cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \"H\u00f4m nay, HAGL ham t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u1edf nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ph\u00eda sau nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Theo t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng dao \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb thua th\u00eam, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00f4m nay r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 31 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 18 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-khanh-hoa-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hagl-vs-khanh-hoa-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-khanh-hoa-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190694.html\">HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a (KT): Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1046","checkdouble":"190717"},{"date":"22:31 08/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">'Con t\u00e0u' H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018. Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 TP.HCM tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, CLB TP.HCM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong kho\u1ea3ng 25 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trung l\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-3 \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/DMH_3858(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP.HCM t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i V-league. V\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi, tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TP.HCM l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a h\u00f2a nhau trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. 'G\u1ed7' v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm song sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V-League r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean V-League \u0111\u1ec3 '\u0103n ng\u1ee7' c\u00f9ng World Cup.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Oseni \u0111ang 't\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i' trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 th\u00ec c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i binh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Tien Linh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/nguyen-tien-linh-xuat-sac-nhat-vleague-thang-5.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Ti\u1ebfn Linh thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Oseni xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 4 b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u00edt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a SLNA. S\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/8/Highlight-Quang-Nam-vs-Binh-Duong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>4. C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1edbi 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 TP.HCM v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t. N\u0103m nay V-League s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1,5 su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1045","checkdouble":"190719"},{"date":"23:02 08/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh' Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/hagl-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-chieu-mo-thu-mon-dt-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng to ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 'minh oan' cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u00ean ch\u1ea1y l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i: '\u0110\u1ee9ng d\u1eady \u0111i, c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u m\u00e0 n\u1eb1m'. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a th\u1ea5y v\u1eady li\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea9y Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn x\u1ea5n l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n n\u00ean b\u1ecb th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u00ean k\u00ecm ch\u1ebf, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi l\u1ebd x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m, khi\u00eau kh\u00edch khi\u1ebfn Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1eefng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1044","checkdouble":"190720"},{"date":"00:11 09/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>1. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 32 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 hai CLB \u1edf nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 TP.HCM.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Diem-nhan-tran-HAGL-2-4-Khanh-Hoa-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a G\u1ed7\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u00e1ch V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd 'G\u1ed7' l\u00ean nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay anh \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00e0 A S\u00e2n. Sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 39 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 44 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Youssouf Toure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, e r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong t\u1ed1p 5 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<h2>2. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, 'G\u1ed7' \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i khi hai t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n th\u1ee9 hai cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb pha treo b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Josip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Osmar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-2, song t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HAGL gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh HAGL ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh gi\u1ecfi trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<h2>3. M\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00f4m nay (8/7) g\u1eb7p Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An khi anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng do l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 22, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c Ngh\u1ec7 An d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m nhanh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea9y ra. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 28, anh l\u1ea1i x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai theo k\u00e8m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. Trong ph\u00fat n\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00ec h\u00f9ng h\u1ed5 g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, khi cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL, CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu l\u00e9p v\u1ebf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd phong t\u1ecfa g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u00edn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh r\u1ed3i m\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Toure c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng s\u1eafc l\u1ea1nh.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t set qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 ngang ph\u00fat 84 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o thay anh l\u00e0 Ho\u00e0i An s\u00fat b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/36787800_1815071101918501_4864050149187387392_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i Pleiku gi\u00fap Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111ang c\u00f3 31 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 19, xem ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c nh\u1ecf, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai chung cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HAGL c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau tr\u1eadn thua v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb SLNA v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean BXH. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi SLNA v\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sinh t\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1043","checkdouble":"190725"},{"date":"01:02 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">'Con t\u00e0u' H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018. Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 TP.HCM tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, CLB TP.HCM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong kho\u1ea3ng 25 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trung l\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-3 \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/DMH_3858(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP.HCM t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i V-league. V\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi, tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TP.HCM l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a h\u00f2a nhau trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. 'G\u1ed7' v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm song sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V-League r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean V-League \u0111\u1ec3 '\u0103n ng\u1ee7' c\u00f9ng World Cup.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Oseni \u0111ang 't\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i' trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 th\u00ec c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i binh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Tien Linh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/nguyen-tien-linh-xuat-sac-nhat-vleague-thang-5.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Ti\u1ebfn Linh thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Oseni xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 4 b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u00edt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a SLNA. S\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/8/Highlight-Quang-Nam-vs-Binh-Duong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>4. C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1edbi 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 TP.HCM v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t. N\u0103m nay V-League s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1,5 su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1042","checkdouble":"190726"},{"date":"01:14 09/07","title":"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TP.HCM, HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/thang-dam-clb-tphcm-hlv-ha-noi-van-khiem-ton-noi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TPHCM, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TPHCM, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Thang-dam-CLB-TPHCM,-HLV-Chu-Dinh-Nghiem-noi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch TP.HCM v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 6-3. Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm V-League 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: \u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80%\".\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam cho r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb khi l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB TP.HCM, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: \"Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 phung ph\u00ed r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn l\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn CLB nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn CLB m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi-168-190726.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi-168-190726.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190695.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TPHCM (KT): Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson l\u1eadp poker trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1041","checkdouble":"190727"},{"date":"06:17 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7: Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-97-choang-voi-doi-hoi-cua-neymar-voi-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/7.\r\n</h2><h2>Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris &ldquo;t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5&rdquo; Edinson Cavani, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luis Suarez &ndash; b\u1edfi Neymar r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 Brazil l\u1eabn Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 97 Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-97-Choang-voi-doi-hoi-cua-Neymar-voi-PSG-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7: Neymar l\u1ea1i ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Paulinho l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Trung Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 sau 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u1ea1i CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y l\u1ea1i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ef1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, cho d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e3i 10 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y (chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paulinho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Fernando Hierro ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt ng\u00e0y sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi La Roja \u1edf c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i quay l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed G\u0110TT c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 chia tay trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Modric chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110ang m\u1ea3i chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Croatia v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf CLB. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh kh\u00f4ng b\u1eadn t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c CR7 s\u1eafp gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Uruguay chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng quay l\u1ea1i Uruguay sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup gi\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, m\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p chuy\u1ebfn bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lucas Torreira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Torreira tranh b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>R\u1ed9 tin Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 Mahrez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man xanh c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo Daily Mail, Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1040","checkdouble":"190728"},{"date":"06:38 09/07","title":"Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/lindelof-tro-lai-mu-sau-that-bai-tai-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n Anh, \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga sau v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2>Lindelof tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Old Trafford<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0), Victor Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ed1t, anh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Lindelof v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110T Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay, v\u00e0 Lindelof s\u1ebd s\u1edbm h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf CLB.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft vang l\u00ean, trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane, c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 Phil Jones, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Marcus Rashford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn an \u1ee7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/lindelof.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Lindelof chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd (c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U), b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u00f4m t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T Anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u1ea1i World Cup, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00fd h\u01a1n khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng&rdquo; &ndash; Lindelof chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, anh s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Jose Mourinho v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</span><br>\r\nSau khi \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Zlatan Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll b\u1edfi Rooney c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1edbi David Beckham.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/214818-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1039","checkdouble":"190729"},{"date":"06:54 09/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, \u0110T B\u1ec9 e ng\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/truoc-dai-chien-voi-phap-dt-bi-e-ngai-mot-cai-ten.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois, v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Kylian Mbappe \u2013 sao tr\u1ebb \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.\r\n</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Mbappe l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9, Nacer Chadli \u0111\u00e3 so s\u00e1nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi Leo Messi. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Messi. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Mbappe, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t nhanh, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cLu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil, b\u1ea1n ch\u1eb3ng e ng\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i s\u1edf, \u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ph\u00e1p. Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Kylian Mbappe tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Kylian Mbappe tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/DT-Bi-to-ra-de-chung-Kylian-Mbappe-truoc-tran-danh-lon-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Kylian Mbappe tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 - ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mbappe l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i nguy h\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea chia s\u1ebb: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e0i cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i. Kylian n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng video v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i, khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i video v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Kylian v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0 l\u1eafm \u0111\u00e2u\u201d \u2013 Hazard cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Vermaelen c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb: \u201cPh\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u00eau th\u00edch cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i xa h\u01a1n, hy v\u1ecdng \u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, HLV Roberto Martinez s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Thomas Meunier. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-ha-guc-brazil-hay-cam-on-premier-league-vi-the-he-vang-421-190575.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/luka.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-ha-guc-brazil-hay-cam-on-premier-league-vi-the-he-vang-421-190575.html\">B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Brazil: H\u00e3y c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Premier League v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nNeymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, trong khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 b\u00e1 v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-mbappe-421-190709.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/DT-Bi-to-ra-de-chung-Kylian-Mbappe-truoc-tran-danh-lon-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-mbappe-421-190709.html\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Mbappe</span><br>\r\nLaurent Blanc ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Les Bleus \u0111\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-uruguay-vs-phap-02-sai-lam-nhung-khoanh-khac-va-giot-nuoc-mat-nghen-ngao-421-190576.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/du-am-uruguay-vs-phap-02-sai-lam-nhung-khoanh-khac-va-giot-nuoc-mat-nghen-ngao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-uruguay-vs-phap-02-sai-lam-nhung-khoanh-khac-va-giot-nuoc-mat-nghen-ngao-421-190576.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay 0-2 Ph\u00e1p: Sai l\u1ea7m, nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc v\u00e0 gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ngh\u1eb9n ng\u00e0o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u1eefa La Celeste v\u00e0 G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1038","checkdouble":"190730"},{"date":"13:37 08/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i qua 7/7.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/7, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia. D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-1 \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan khi\u1ebfn nguy c\u01a1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hoang Anh Tuan\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;V\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y xem nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mong \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng U19 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 fair-play \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U19 Singapore. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp hay kh\u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1eabn kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18/10 t\u1edbi 4/11/2018.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00dac v\u00e0 Jordan. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190633.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-1 U19 Indonesia (Gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1eb9p \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y sau khi ch\u00fang ta thua U19 Indonesia, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay-372-190607.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay-372-190607.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-1 U19 Indonesia (KT): T\u00ednh to\u00e1n sai l\u1ea7m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i sau khi ch\u00fang ta thua U19 Indonesia, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1037","checkdouble":"190686"},{"date":"13:42 08/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/nhan-dinh-quang-nam-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-87-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7 (V\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 87 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 87 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/quang-nam-vs-binh-duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e3 6 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng xo\u00e1y tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng khi gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng bao nhi\u00eau. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 to\u00e0n h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua trong 4 l\u1ea7n ra qu\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 1 b\u1eadc tr\u00ean BXH. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n \u1edf ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ecf ra nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 thua t\u1edbi 1-3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Thanh Trung v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam: V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng, Huy H\u00f9ng, V\u0103n H\u00e0, Thanh H\u01b0ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1eafng, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Thanh Trung, H\u1eefu Ph\u01b0\u1edbc, Thiago, V\u0103n H\u1ecdc, T\u1ea5n Sinh.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Thanh Th\u1ea3o, H.T.T\u00e0i, Xu\u00e2n Lu\u00e2n, Anh T\u00e0i, L.T.T\u00e0i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, Tanidis, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n V\u0169, Ho\u00e0ng Max.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1036","checkdouble":"190687"},{"date":"14:00 08/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 18h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/nhan-dinh-quang-ninh-vs-can-tho-18h00-ngay-87-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h